Name: hwpy
Version: 0.2.1
Summary: Show Linux Hardware Info
Home-page: https://github.com/starsliao/hwpy
Author: Stars Liao
Author-email: starsliao@163.com
License: MIT Licence
Description: # install(python2.7 and python3.x)
        
        #### lastest psutil maybe required
        ```
        # yum install -y gcc python-devel
        # pip install -U setuptools 
        # pip install -U psutil
        ```
        
        ```
        # pip install hwpy
        ```
        
        # usage
        ```
        # python -m hwpy
        ```
        ```
        from hwpy import info
        info.main()
        info.hwlist
        ```
        ```
        info.cpu
        info.net    
        info.disk
        info.part   
        info.host
        info.mem
        ```
        
